content.description: This is a chimney route between a large pylon and a retaining wall. It tapers upward.
content.location: On the retaining wall north of Commonwealth Ave, the pylon/chimney is located on the northern side of the Tall Wall.

pathTokens: Kenmore Walls aka Back Bay Fens

content.description:
Tall Wall is 17 feet high and is located off Beacon St. near Commonwealth Ave. near the Charles River. 

  L->R:

North Face

  A. Cornerback, 10   B. Broken Back, 9   C. Out Back, 9   D. West End, 11+ (eliminate)
